{"tid":2355313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[估國家] 空姐與11男跨年趴遭集體性侵！傷痕累累慘死浴缸　最後身影曝光","createTime":"2021-01-06T04:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:25:10.000Z","uid":17387,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4fc6e6575bd140c2e4bd6ab6c2555b937f5b4e","tid":2355313,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"菲律賓一名23歲空姐兼網美達賽拉(Christine Angelica Dacera)，在日前參加新年派對時，竟被發現慘死飯店浴缸中，而且身上傷痕累累，下體還呈現撕裂傷。警方初步研判達賽拉生前遭到集體性侵，並鎖定與她一同開趴的11名男子，目前已有3人被逮捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Nt7ErGwn_9Tue2OereupWrcqnkQ=/1280x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YPG3RM25WBH7LK5R3MGUMMDWGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNt7ErGwn_9Tue2OereupWrcqnkQ%3D%2F1280x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYPG3RM25WBH7LK5R3MGUMMDWGI.jpg&h=76786c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《CNN》與《Attracttour》報導，去年12月31日，達賽拉和一群好友到高級飯店「城市花園酒店」(City Garden Hotel)租下一間高級房間開跨年趴，監視器畫面也拍到，達賽拉與一群男生在飯店走廊上交流熱絡，隨後大家走進房間中。但在本月1日早上，其中一名參加者加利達(Rommel Galida)發現達賽拉倒臥在浴缸中，且全身發黑，達賽拉雖然之後被緊急送醫，但醫師仍在1日下午5時宣告達賽拉死亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/eK0avNvzwQYcL_rvvYXU5dHQw-s=/1280x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P7KMZXKFHFGE7G34WNFIGZMMDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeK0avNvzwQYcL_rvvYXU5dHQw-s%3D%2F1280x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP7KMZXKFHFGE7G34WNFIGZMMDA.jpg&h=eae37cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方介入調查後發現，達賽拉身上傷痕累累，尤其大腿處與膝蓋有多重瘀青與割痕，下體也有撕裂傷並殘留精液，警方初步認為達賽拉遭到集體性侵。不過達賽拉的家屬抱怨，警方雖然在口頭報告中提及性侵，但在正式的案情與驗屍報告中，卻指出達賽拉的死因是「主動脈瘤破裂」自然死亡，更草率地對外發表「已結案」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/8aBhsBPhIKdfE_jx6JmteLO5Jow=/634x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PQVHVXPDIZBELKT4COSC7ABQR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8aBhsBPhIKdfE_jx6JmteLO5Jow%3D%2F634x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPQVHVXPDIZBELKT4COSC7ABQR4.jpg&h=618b8596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/m15fDeg3g2jVwJeFg5xEAIeGCPo=/750x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MGMULB6ZJZAGLP5EW3THCJPTTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm15fDeg3g2jVwJeFg5xEAIeGCPo%3D%2F750x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMGMULB6ZJZAGLP5EW3THCJPTTQ.jpg&h=5a8a09e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家屬認為，警方隱瞞了部分案件實情，未提及達賽拉的外傷狀況，因此要求再進行一次驗屍。達賽拉的母親夏蓉(Sharon)堅信，女兒的死並不單純，她們想要證明達賽拉絕對不是自然死亡，夏蓉也痛心地說：「無論你們(指性侵犯)對我女兒做出多麼骯髒的事，她都不應該被這樣對待！」在家屬的極力要求下，警方也將當天和達賽拉一同開跨年趴的11名男子，全部列為嫌疑人，目前已逮捕3人，還有8人在逃。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/SntzfkvqZQpeGVNziyJXQC1zSo8=/720x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YUOSEZA7XBAIRPKJBP4UUBIPIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSntzfkvqZQpeGVNziyJXQC1zSo8%3D%2F720x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYUOSEZA7XBAIRPKJBP4UUBIPIQ.jpg&h=42749e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一方面，達賽拉之死的消息曝光後，這兩日引發菲律賓網路鄉民的熱烈討論，不少網友挺達賽拉與母親夏蓉，認為所有女性都應該不再被欺負，「所有女性都不該沉默」。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"43f3cf5e541d6cdec7ef6279ead639b250293dc1","tid":2355313,"uid":17387,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"一個女仔同十一個男人倒數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太危險了"},{"pid":"2c1ec7450b6f414f67d272a76e397ec37c1786bc","tid":2355313,"uid":81214,"like":23,"dislike":7,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"11個男人點分??<br />\n屎眼 閪 口 左右手 都係應付到5條賓周"},{"pid":"454c442b94cfa21fad6d2fe3c3cb914630adae52","tid":2355313,"uid":238973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"點解做愛都會做到整死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a1da73918e20b8f494b95c78ea3cf53d25e921","tid":2355313,"uid":279326,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"做雞做到命都無埋　唉"},{"pid":"4409d7a7c25db3a03dfbae29a275f9e205a2d620","tid":2355313,"uid":62,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"454c442b94cfa21fad6d2fe3c3cb914630adae52","tid":2355313,"uid":238973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"點解做愛都會做到整死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"出血過多無人理"},{"pid":"0c40e9c329a9fdc6928dd228ced6b5f3a2f26cf9","tid":2355313,"uid":35712,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"非常時期拉日常post 推時事"},{"pid":"88bb83c192762ca901d7870f5340bc15cf0b5084","tid":2355313,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4409d7a7c25db3a03dfbae29a275f9e205a2d620","tid":2355313,"uid":62,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"454c442b94cfa21fad6d2fe3c3cb914630adae52","tid":2355313,"uid":238973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"點解做愛都會做到整死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"出血過多無人理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"點解會做到出血 同埋都唔call醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as